Detailed Description

The BarcodeReader Channel's delegate methods.

These methods should be implemented by the ICBarCodeReader's delegate in order to be notified of its events. Only "barcodeData" method is required.
You should also implement the unsuccessfulDecode method to alert the user when the scanner fails to decode a barcode.
